ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model

Class LinAxis

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.APhysicalComponent
      • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.LinAxis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Floodable

    public class LinAxis
extends APhysicalComponent
implements Floodable
    General linear axis model class. Implements the physical model of a linear axis. From the input parameter translational speed and process force, the requested motor torque is calculated Assumptions: The inertia of mass and frictional forces are negligible Inputlist: 1: State : [-] : State of the axis (0/1) 2: Speed : [Hz] : Actual rotational speed 3: ProcessForce : [N] : Actual process force along the axis 4: CoolantIn : [-] : Coolant fluid in Outputlist: 1: PTotal : [W] : Input power 2: PUse : [W] : Output power (usable) 3: PLoss : [W] : Output power (losses) 4: CoolantOut : [-] : Coolant fluid out Config parameters: Transmission : [m] : Transmission between the motor (rpm) and the translation (mm_min) Mass : [kg] : Mass of the moving part Alpha : [deg] : Angle between the axis and the vertical of the machine StructureMass StructureMaterial StructureDuct
    Author:
    simon
